WEBVTT

17:37.720 --> 17:38.350 line:80%
Mr. Wang,

17:38.520 --> 17:40.040 line:80%
we haven't found the mastermind yet.

17:40.040 --> 17:42.300 line:80%
How could they close the case so hastily?

17:42.660 --> 17:43.960 line:80%
The people who died
in the pine forest were

17:43.960 --> 17:44.830 line:80%
the culprits.

17:45.610 --> 17:48.310 line:80%
They were bandits
from the Qingfeng Stronghold.
